Delicious Fright	KEY:Witch Major Hex ~ Delicious Fright	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Witch Class Feature.SpecialQuality.WitchHex.MajorHex	PREVARGTEQ:WitchHexAbilityLVL,10	SOURCEPAGE:p.15	DESC:The witch can feed on the fear of her victim. The target of this hex becomes shaken for a number of rounds equal to 3 + the witch's Intelligence modifier. As long as the witch remains within 30 feet of her target, she gains a + i morale bonus on attack rolls and a +i morale bonus on saving throws as long as this effect persists. A successful Will save reduces the duration of this hex to i round. This is a mind-affecting fear effect.

